nodes.title: Image upscale and sharpen before 2nd pass
Links to the upscale models
widgets_values:
Put them into models/upscale_models folder

[2xhigurashi v1 compact](https://openmodeldb.info/models/2x-Higurashi-v1-compact) - this is an anime focused upscaler but fast

[4xClear reality v1](https://openmodeldb.info/models/4x-ClearRealityV1) - a fast ppl focused upscaler

[4xDF2K_JPEG](https://openmodeldb.info/models/4x-realsr-df2k-jpeg) - a slower but better quality upscaler

[1xDeJPG](https://openmodeldb.info/models/1x-DeJPG-realplksr-otf) - one of my favorite enhancer model

[1xSkinContrast](https://openmodeldb.info/models/1x-SkinContrast-HighAlternative-SuperUltraCompact) - This model has 3 variations. I only tried this one yet
